column5: Ok, so now we have a standard to meet for next winter's Sturgeon Lake's Ice hut. So who wants in?
Question # 1 Cliff.. do you have a good source for brass???
What a great story.  Two sayings come to mine:  You can't take it with you and you only go around once.  Inspiring!
And if he has the brass... does he have the goods to use with it
With a "hut" like that, I wouldn't go home til ice out
i think i would take up ice fishing if this was the norm....way kewl!!!!!
I saw  these at the Montreal Sportsman's Show today.            Also met Carll2 there from L'Aventurier on the Gouin..Marc thorpe was there and even said hello to Dave Mercer....who'da thunk it....
